            "text": "At about 8:40 pm a called was placed for the accident, with Rehoboth Beach Volunteer Fire Co. responding. They were kind enough to snap some photos for the rest of us to enjoy. From them we can see serious damage to the front fascia. There could definitely be some serious chassis damage, but at least the mid-engine configuration likely protected most if not all of the powertrain.",
